{
  "stem": "12051.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He had a voice that any artist in the United States can't compare with him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was an artist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He painted.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a young fellow, in Poland, Bielitz was a textile manufacturing city.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had connections.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was doing designs for British companies, textile companies, and they used his designs to manufacture material.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was very, very talented.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "God knows why he did it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Who knows?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, did you know what happened to him during the war?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was picked in Wieliczka yet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm going back and forth-- why I'm going back to it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In Wieliczka, there, when they made the city judenrein, they picked certain people out that they should go to another city to run the [GERMAN] in Bochnia.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, in the meantime, as they were--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bochnia is a city.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's workshops.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] On the way to Bochnia-- there was a fire in Bochnia.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they called it sabotage, that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they took all those people, the whole trainload, and shipped them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And nobody knows what happened to them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were all killed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "To this day, I'm searching for him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Whenever I see a group of people, whether it's in the movies, whether it's a gathering, I always look.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Maybe I will find him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because he still might have the same name.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I have changed mine because I am married.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I'm in search of him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I think I will search to the rest of my days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After Prokocim, we went to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Plaszow was called Julag Number I.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's called Juden Lager Number I, which was a, a subsidiary to the camp that was called also Plaszow, where Goeth was in charge.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Goeth couldn't stand it that there is another camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
